Didn't work before; works now. 

Code I use for unpickling:

``` python
@provide_session
def unpickle_dag(dag_id, session=None):
    orm_dag = (
        session.query(DagModel)
        .filter(DagModel.dag_id == dag_id)
        ).first()

    if orm_dag:
        orm_pickle = (
            session.query(DagPickle)
            .filter(DagPickle.id == orm_dag.pickle_id)
            ).first()

        if orm_pickle:
            return orm_pickle.pickle
```

